            "body": "Thanks for the pointer!\n\nThe settings from [the new docs](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/c53fb58c15c365b41db893416483b3e38f3db79c/runtime/doc/options.txt#L5518-L5526) work for me (still in v0.11.5).\n\nI also tried installing pwsh and [the additional settings](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/c53fb58c15c365b41db893416483b3e38f3db79c/runtime/doc/options.txt#L5527-L5533) work too. Although, it'd probably be clearer if `let &shell = 'pwsh'` was included in the code block with `shellcmdflag`. I copypasted wrong and didn't realized I'd failed to set pwsh.",
